      .wear-comparison-card
        %h3 コンプレッションウェアとは？
        .dotted-line
        .wear-comparison-card-inner
          .wear-comparison-card-inner-text-conteiner
            %p 高機能インナーとは、着用するだけで保温・冷感・筋肉や体幹のサポート・姿勢矯正…
            = image_tag 'icon01.gif', class: "next-img"
            %span 続きを見る
          .wear-comparison-card-inner-img-conteiner
            = image_tag 'bg_02.gif', class: "wear-comparison-card-inner-img"
      .wear-comparison-card
        %h3 高機能インナーとは？
        .dotted-line
        .wear-comparison-card-inner
          .wear-comparison-card-inner-text-conteiner
            %p 高機能インナーとは、着用するだけで保温・冷感・筋肉や体幹のサポート・姿勢矯正・疲労回復…
            = image_tag 'icon01.gif', class: "next-img"
            %span 続きを見る
          .wear-comparison-card-inner-img-conteiner
            = image_tag 'bg_03.gif', class: "wear-comparison-card-inner-img"
      .wear-comparison-card
        %h3 トレーニングウェアの選び方
        .dotted-line
        .wear-comparison-card-inner
          .wear-comparison-card-inner-text-conteiner
            %p トレーニングをする際、ウェアの選び方によってトレーニング効果も変わってきます…
            = image_tag 'icon01.gif', class: "next-img"
            %span 続きを見る
          .wear-comparison-card-inner-img-conteiner
            = image_tag 'bg_04.gif', class: "wear-comparison-card-inner-img"
      .wear-comparison-card
        %h3 フィットネスウェアの選び方
